yle="border-bottom: 1px dotted;"><span title="/i/: 'y' trong 'happy'">i</span><span title="/ə/: 'a' trong 'about'">ə</span></span>/</a></span><small class="nowrap">&nbsp;(<span class="metadata audiolink"><a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0e/En-au-Australia.ogg" class="internal" title="En-au-Australia.ogg" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: url(&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/13px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png&quot;) !important; background-position: left center !important; background-size: 13px !important; background-repeat: no-repeat !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; padding-left: 16px !important; padding-right: 0px !important;">nghe</a></span>)</small></span>,<sup id="cite_ref-15" class="reference" style="line-height: 1em; font-size: 11.2px; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%9Ac#cite_note-15" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">[13]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-16" class="reference" style="line-height: 1em; font-size: 11.2px; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%9Ac#cite_note-16" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">[14]</a></sup>), tên chính thức là&nbsp;<b>Thịnh vượng chung Úc</b>&nbsp;(<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ti%E1%BA%BFng_Anh" title="Tiếng Anh" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">tiếng Anh</a>:&nbsp;<i><span lang="en">Commonwealth of Australia</span></i><sup id="cite_ref-17" class="reference" style="line-height: 1em; font-size: 11.2px; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%9Ac#cite_note-17" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">[15]</a></sup>), là một&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qu%E1%BB%91c_gia" title="Quốc gia" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">quốc gia</a>&nbsp;có&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danh_s%C3%A1ch_qu%E1%BB%91c_gia_c%C3%B3_ch%E1%BB%A7_quy%E1%BB%81n" title="Danh sách quốc gia có chủ quyền" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">chủ quyền</a>&nbsp;bao gồm&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%E1%BB%A5c_%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba_%C3%9Ac" title="Lục địa Úc" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Lục địa Úc</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o" title="Đảo" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">đảo</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tasmania" title="Tasmania" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Tasmania</a>&nbsp;và các đảo khác nhỏ hơn. Đây là&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danh_s%C3%A1ch_qu%E1%BB%91c_gia_theo_di%E1%BB%87n_t%C3%ADch" title="Danh sách quốc gia theo diện tích" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">quốc gia lớn thứ 6 trên thế giới về diện tích</a>. Các quốc gia lân cận của Úc gồm có&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia" title="Indonesia" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Indonesia</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%90%C3%B4ng_Timor" title="Đông Timor" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Đông Timor</a>&nbsp;và&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papua_New_Guinea" title="Papua New Guinea" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Papua New Guinea</a>&nbsp;ở phía bắc, các&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qu%E1%BA%A7n_%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o_Solomon" title="Quần đảo Solomon" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">quần đảo Solomon</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanuatu" title="Vanuatu" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Vanuatu</a>, và&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nouvelle-Cal%C3%A9donie" title="Nouvelle-Calédonie" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Nouvelle-Calédonie</a>&nbsp;thuộc&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ph%C3%A1p" title="Pháp" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Pháp</a>&nbsp;ở phía đông bắc và&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Zealand" title="New Zealand" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">New Zealand</a>&nbsp;ở phía đông nam.&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%E1%BB%A7_%C4%91%C3%B4" title="Thủ đô" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Thủ đô</a>&nbsp;của Úc là&nbsp;<a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canberra" title="Canberra" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; backgroun